<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

    <title>Document</title>
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Work+Sans:wght@400;600&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
  </head>
  <style>
    @media (min-width: 750px) {
      body {
        width: 450px;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
      }
    }
    .parent {
      background-color: white;
      padding-top: 20px;
      padding-bottom: 20px;
      padding-left: 10px;
      padding-right: 10px;
      color: black;
    }
    .logo {
      width: 51px;
    }
    .heading {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 600;
      line-height: 28px;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }
    .hello {
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 500;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }
    .name {
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    .text {
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 400;
      line-height: 20px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .background {
      margin-top: 10px;
    }
    .heading2 {
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 20px;
    }
    .link {
      color: orange;
    }
    .social {
      display: flex;
      gap: 12px;
    }
    .footer {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      margin-top: 50px;
    }
    .socialIcon {
      width: 24px;
    }
    a {
      text-decoration: none;
    }
  </style>
  <body style="font-family: 'Work Sans', sans-serif">
    <div class="parent">
      <div>
        <img
          class="logo w-[51px]"
          src="<%- base_url %>/assets/mail/logo4.png"
        />
      </div>
      <h4 class="heading">
        Your Clarity Assessment overall score is <%- score %>%
      </h4>
      <h4 class="hello">Hello <span class="name"> <%- first_name %></span>,</h4>
      <h4 class="text">
        Clarity is in phases, and no matter the phase you are in, your clarity
        can deepen so that you can achieve better outcomes and we are ready to
        work with you to become the best version of yourself.
      </h4>
      <h4 class="text">
        As a next step, our team is offering you a customized coaching
        experience through any this pathway that we recommend for you:
      </h4>
      <div class="background">
        <img src="<%- base_url %>/assets/mail/discovery.png" />
      </div>
      <h4 class="heading2">Discovering the New You</h4>
      <h4 class="text">
        This coaching package empowers you to embrace change, unlock hidden
        talents, and pursue paths aligned with your authentic self. The courses
        in this package include removing blocks to your clarity,
        discovering/unleashing a new version of you, leadership, and
        accountability. To sign up,
        <a href="<%- base_url %>/discovering-assessment" target="_blank">
          <span class="link"> here</span> </a
        >.
      </h4>
      <h4 class="text">We look forward to welcoming you!</h4>
      <h4 class="text">
        Keep transforming,<br />The Bimbo Mesele Coaching Team
      </h4>
      <div class="footer">
        <div class="social">
          <a
            href="https://www.instagram.com/bimbomeselecoaching?igsh=MWo1c2VvdTZ3eDNodQ=="
            target="_blank"
          >
            <div>
              <img
                class="socialIcon"
                src="<%- base_url %>/assets/mail/instagram.png"
              />
            </div>
          </a>

          <a
            href="https://www.facebook.com/bimbomeselecoaching"
            target="_blank"
          >
            <div>
              <img
                class="socialIcon"
                src="<%- base_url %>/assets/mail/facebook.png"
              />
            </div>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
